# TodoWeatherAuth

A beautifully designed **Todo App** integrated with **OpenWeather API** that helps users manage tasks while keeping an eye on the weatherâ€”especially useful for outdoor activities. The app also includes a fake login/logout system using **Redux Toolkit (RTK)** and supports light/dark themes.

Live Demo: [todo-weather-auth.vercel.app](https://todo-weather-auth.vercel.app)

GitHub Repo: [TodoWeatherAuth](https://github.com/SachinSinghPatwal/TodoWeatherAuth.git)

